snippet.title: NBA LIVE 18 Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Play NBA LIVE 18, featuring THE ONE, an NBA career journey defined by the shots you take and choices you make, plus much more, on PS4 and Xbox One. Available on September 15.

Follow no one. Be the one.

Don't miss an NBA LIVE 18 video. Subscribe: http://bit.ly/2s0gXzT

Learn more about NBA Live 18: https://www.easports.com/nba-live/features
